件中散单业务增长低于预期。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b95e26d901490ed1172e9f19417f13b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453657036"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8+PQlJujuepQEAMaCDYzMDkyMjk5ILm+voMGMAo4xA1AK3IJNDUzNjU3MDM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1618014480.7005951", "card_id": "Q_453502948", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 153}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待郑州在新一线的收入排名倒数第三？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "根据公开资料梳理统计 15 个新一线城市居民人均可支配收入数据发现，苏州在 15 个新一线城市中人均收入水平最高。有 5 个城市 2020 年人均收入超过了 5 万元大关，其中有 3 个城市超过了 6 万元大关，这三个城市全部来自长三角。三个城市收入低于 4 万元大关，分别是西部的重庆、西安以及来自中部地区的郑州。其中，郑州全体居民人均可支配收入 36661 元，在 15 个城市中位列第 13 位，仅高过重庆和西安。你怎么看？郑州人均收入新一线城市倒数第三"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a6f56abed34cadccdf3ca750588c69ea_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "44 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453502948"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8+PQlJujuepQEAMaCDYzMDU3OTY1INLZuYMGMBM46AVALHIJNDUzNTAyOTQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1618014480.7010796", "card_id": "Q_24601021", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 543}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待香港一年制硕士？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "考试难度如何？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-391c8670f4be7247678595858f05386a_hd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/24601021"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I8+PQlJujuepQEAMaBzIwMjI1MTAg1/LCngUwDDiCcEAtcggyNDYwMTAyMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1618014480.7014453",